      "author_association" : "CONTRIBUTOR",
      "body" : "Why read the block from disk twice when `verbosity <= 0` ?\r\n1. in the `if (verbosity <= 0 && !RPCSerializationFlags()) {}` to `raw_block`\r\n2. with `block = GetBlockChecked(pblockindex);`\r\n",
